summary: first dungeon for examination by public
descriptionHtml:
Just a small dungeon with some enemies, traps and presents made from the bethesda tutorial series.
Don't expect to much. It is more a test for myself and friends.
It is my first mission and I hope it is an usefull style and the difficulty is acceptable.

If you want to try it:
You can find the dungeon in the soutn west to Falkreath.

[img]https://picload.org/image/doagaidr/map_falkreath.jpg[/img]

plz leave a comment

More soon.
author: MrNiceKai
